                             "vaso de press√£o"@pt-br ;
                  annotation:firstOrderLogicAxiom "‚àÄx (PressureVessel(x) ‚Üí Assembly(x))" ;
                  annotation:isPrimitive "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
                  annotation:naturalLanguageDefinition "A closed assembly designed to hold fluids at a pressure substantially different from ambient, with a shell rated to withstand the resulting mechanical stress."@en ,
                                                       "Um conjunto fechado projetado para conter fluidos a uma press√£o substancialmente diferente da ambiente, com casco classificado para suportar a tens√£o mec√¢nica resultante."@pt-br ;
                  annotation:primitiveRationale "A diferen√ßa estrutural de conten√ß√£o de press√£o (casco classificado, especifica√ß√£o de tens√£o mec√¢nica) √© expressa informalmente na NLD; OWL carrega apenas o g√™nero (Assembly). Axiomas estruturais s√£o adiados ao Incremento 2b."@pt-br ,
                                                "The pressure-containing structural differentia (rated shell, mechanical stress specification) is expressed informally in the NLD; OWL carries only the genus (Assembly). Structural axioms are deferred to Incremento 2b."@en ;
                  annotation:semiFormalNaturalLanguageAxiom "if x is a 'pressure vessel' then x is an 'assembly'"@en ,
                                                            "se x √© um 'vaso de press√£o', ent√£o x √© um 'conjunto'"@pt-br .


