                  annotation:primitiveRationale "A diferen√ßa estrutural de detec√ß√£o-ou-medi√ß√£o √© expressa informalmente na NLD; OWL carrega apenas o g√™nero (MaterialArtifact). O eixo estrutural (Instrument) √© ortogonal ao eixo funcional (MeasurementInstrument); um artefato √© ambos simultaneamente ‚Äî intencional (ODR-018)."@pt-br ,
                                                "The sensing-or-measuring structural differentia is expressed informally in the NLD; OWL carries only the genus (MaterialArtifact). The structural axis (Instrument) is orthogonal to the functional axis (MeasurementInstrument); an artifact is both simultaneously ‚Äî intended (ODR-018)."@en ;
                  annotation:semiFormalNaturalLanguageAxiom "if x is an 'instrument' then x is a 'material artifact'"@en ,
